### MiMo — REST Client request collection
### Install: humao.rest-client  (VS Code extension: "REST Client")
### Click "Send Request" above each block, or Ctrl+Alt+R on the cursor.
### Vars are pulled from .env.local via the dotenv section of settings below.

@base = https://api.xiaomimimo.com/v1
@key  = {{$dotenv MIMO_API_KEY}}
@model = mimo-v2-flash

### 1. List entitled models
GET {{base}}/models
api-key: {{key}}

### 2. One-shot chat
POST {{base}}/chat/completions
api-key: {{key}}
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{model}}",
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Give me 3 dev-ops tips for a React/Vite app." }
  ],
  "max_completion_tokens": 512,
  "stream": false
}

### 3. Streamed chat (SSE) — response pane will show each `data:` chunk
POST {{base}}/chat/completions
api-key: {{key}}
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{model}}",
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Stream a 5-line haiku about Postgres." }
  ],
  "max_completion_tokens": 256,
  "stream": true
}

### 4. Chat with system prompt + JSON-mode response
POST {{base}}/chat/completions
api-key: {{key}}
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "mimo-v2-pro",
  "messages": [
    { "role": "system", "content": "You are a precise code reviewer. Reply as JSON." },
    { "role": "user", "content": "Review this snippet: const add = (a,b)=>a-b;" }
  ],
  "max_completion_tokens": 512,
  "response_format": { "type": "json_object" },
  "temperature": 0.2,
  "stream": false
}

### 5. Thinking mode (mimo-v2-pro supports `thinking`)
POST {{base}}/chat/completions
api-key: {{key}}
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "mimo-v2-pro",
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Prove informally that the empty set is a subset of every set." }
  ],
  "thinking": { "type": "enabled" },
  "max_completion_tokens": 1024,
  "stream": false
}

### 6. Text-to-speech (mimo-v2-tts) — returns base64 audio payload
POST {{base}}/chat/completions
api-key: {{key}}
content-type: application/json

{
  "model": "mimo-v2-tts",
  "messages": [
    { "role": "assistant", "content": "Neural link established. Ready for transmission." }
  ],
  "audio": { "format": "mp3", "voice": "default" },
  "max_completion_tokens": 1024,
  "stream": false
}
